ority of India |publisher=Aai.aero |date=14 January 2015 |accessdate=17 April 2017 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140618154837/http://www.aai.aero/allAirports/airports.jsp |archivedate=18 June 2014  }}</ref> as per the table below\n#'''Role'''&nbsp;\u2013 Role of the airport as given by the table below\n{|class=wikitable\n|+Category of Airport\n|-\n!style=\"width:100px;\"|Category\n!style=\"width:300px;\"|Description\n|-\n|style=\"background:#E0CEF2;\"|'''[[Customs Airport|Customs]]'''||Airports with Customs Checking and Clearance Facilities handling international flights but not elevated to International Airport status.\n|-\n|style=\"background:#CEF2E0;\"|'''Defence'''||Indian Armed Forces Handled Airport\n|-\n|style=\"background:#2F847C;\"|'''[[Domestic Airport|Domestic]]'''||Handles domestic flights\n|-\n| style=\"background:#0ff;\"|'''Future'''||Proposed or Under Construction\n|-\n|style=\"background:#9F8170;\"|'''[[International Airport|International]]'''||Handles International Flights\n|-\n|style=\"background:#CEE0F2;\"|'''Private'''||Private airport for specific purposes\n|}\n{|class=wikitable\n|+Role of Airport\n|-\n!Role\n!Description\n|-\n|[[Civil enclave]]||Civil Enclaves in a Military Airport. Handles Commercial Flights\n|-\n|style=\"background:#A0ACB8\"|Closed||No longer in operation for Commercial Flights\n|-\n|Commercial||Handles Commercial flights\n|-\n|[[Airbase]]||Military Airbase\n|-\n|[[Flight Training|Flying School]]||Airport used to train commercial and/or fighter pilots\n|}\n\n{|class=wikitable\n|-\n|rowspan=2|Commercial service||style=\"background:#ffe6b7;\"|Airport has commercial service\n|-\n| style=\"background:ivory;\"|Airport has no commercial service\n|}\n\n==List==\n\n===[[Andaman and Nicobar Islands]]===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:90%;\"\n|-\n!style=\"width:15%;\"|City Served\n!style=\"width:35%;\"|Airport Name\n!style=\"width:10%;\"|ICAO\n!style=\"width:10%;\"|IATA\n!style=\"width:10%