ore]]|| style=\"background:ivory;\"|[[Nellore Airport]]||align=center|\u2014||align=center|\u2014||colspan=2 style=\"background:#0ff;\"|Future\n|-\n|[[Puttaparthi]]|| style=\"background:ivory;\"|[[Sri Sathya Sai Airport]]||align=center|VOPN||align=center|PUT|| style=\"background:#CEE0F2;\"|Private ||\n|-\n|[[Rajahmundry]]||style=\"background:#ffe6b7;\"|[[Rajahmundry Airport]]||align=center|VORY||align=center|RJA ||style=\"background:#2F847C;\"|Domestic ||Commercial\n|-\n|[[Tirupati]] ||style=\"background:#ffe6b7;\"|[[Tirupati Airport]]||align=center|VOTP||align=center|TIR||style=\"background:#2f847c;\"| Domestic||Commercial\n|-\n|[[Vijayawada]]||style=\"background:#ffe6b7;\"|[[Vijayawada Airport]] ||align=center|VOBZ||align=center|VGA ||style=\"background:#2f847c;\"|Domestic {{ref label|a|VG}} ||Commercial\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[Visakhapatnam]]||style=\"background:#ffe6b7;\"|[[Visakhapatnam Airport|Visakhapatnam International Airport]] ||align=center|VOVZ||align=center|VTZ||style=\"background:#9F8170;\"|International ||Civil Enclave\n|-\n|[[Bhogapuram Airport]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://centreforaviation.com/data/profiles/newairports/bhogapuram-airport|title=Bhogapuram Airport|publisher=CAPA|access-date=5 March 2019}}</ref>||align=center|\u2014||align=center|\u2014||colspan=2 style=\"background:#0ff;\"|Future\n|}\n{{note label|a|VG}} Previously The Airport used to serve a restricted International Airport but now serving only domestic destinations.\n\n===[[Arunachal Pradesh]]===\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:90%;\"\n|-\n!style=\"width:15%;\"|City Served\n!style=\"width:35%;\"|Airport Name\n!style=\"width:10%;\"|ICAO\n!style=\"width:10%;\"|IATA\n!style=\"width:10%;\"|Category\n!style=\"width:15%;\"|Role\n|-\n||[[Along, Arunachal Pradesh|Along]]||style=\"background:ivory;\"|[[Along Airport]]||align=center|VEAN||align=center|IXV||Domestic ||style=\"background:#a0acb8;\"|No scheduled flights\n|-\n|[[Daporijo]]|| style=\"background:ivory;\"|[[Daporijo Airport]