achen]]||style=\"background:ivory;\"|Siachen Air Force Station||align=center|\u2014||align=center|\u2014||style=\"background:#CEF2E0;\"|Defence||Air Base\n|-\n|[[Thoise]]||style=\"background:ivory;\"|[[Thoise|Thoise Airbase]]||align=center|VI57||align=center|\u2014||style=\"background:#CEF2E0;\"|Defence||Air Base\n|}\n\n===[[Lakshadweep]]===\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:90%;\"\n|-\n!style=\"width:15%;\"|City Served\n!style=\"width:30%;\"|Airport Name\n!style=\"width:10%;\"|ICAO\n!style=\"width:10%;\"|IATA\n!style=\"width:10%;\"|Category\n!style=\"width:10%;\"|Role\n|-\n|[[Lakshadweep]]||style=\"background:#ffe6b7;\"|[[Agatti Airport]] || align=center|VOAT||align=center|AGX || style=\"background:#2F847C;\"|Domestic|| Commercial\n|}\n\n===[[Madhya Pradesh]]===\n{{see|List of airports in Madhya Pradesh}}\n\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:90%;\"\n|-\n!style=\"width:15%;\"|City Served\n!style=\"width:30%;\"|Airport Name\n!style=\"width:10%;\"|ICAO\n!style=\"width:10%;\"|IATA\n!style=\"width:10%;\"|Category\n!style=\"width:15%;\"|Role\n|-\n|[[Bhopal]]||style=\"background:#ffe6b7;\"|[[Raja Bhoj Airport]]|| align=\"center\" |VABP||align=center|BHO ||style=\"background:#2F847C;\"|Domestic||Commercial\n|-\n|[[Chhindwara]]|| style=\"background: ivory;\" |Chhindwara Airport|| align=\"center\" |\u2014||align=center|CHD||Domestic||style=\"background:#A0ACB8\"|Closed\n|-\n|[[Gwalior]]||style=\"background:#ffe6b7;\"| [[Gwalior Airport]]|| align=\"center\" |VIGR||align=center|GWL ||style=\"background:#2F847C;\"|Domestic||Commercial\n|-\n|[[Indore]]|| style=\"background:#ffe6b7;\" |[[Devi Ahilya Bai Holkar Airport]] || align=\"center\" |VAID||align=center|IDR ||style=\"background:#9F8170;\"|International<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.businesstoday.in/sectors/aviation/madhya-pradesh-gets-its-first-international-flight-with-indore-dubai-service/story/364643.html|title=Madhya Pradesh gets its first international flight with Indore-Dubai service | work=Bus