ragpur]]|| style=\"background:ivory;\"|[[Kalaikunda Air Force Station]]||align=center|VEDX||align=center|\u2014||style=\"background:#CEF2E0;\"|Defence||Air Base\n|-\n|[[Kolkata]]||style=\"background:#ffe6b7;\"|[[Netaji Subhas Chandra Bose International Airport]]||align=center|VECC||align=center|CCU ||style=\"background:#9F8170;\"|International<ref name=\":1\" /> ||Commercial\n|-\n|[[Malda City|Malda]]|| style=\"background:ivory;\"|[[Malda Airport]]||align=center|VEMH||align=center|LDA||Domestic||style=\"background:#A0ACB8\"|Closed\n|-\n|[[Panagarh]]|| style=\"background:ivory;\"|[[Panagarh Airport]]||align=center|VEPH||align=center|\u2014||style=\"background:#CEF2E0;\"|Defence||Airbase\n|-\n|[[Purulia]]|| style=\"background:ivory;\"|[[Charra Airfield]]|| align=center|\u2014||align=center|\u2014||style=\"background:#CEF2E0;\"|Defence ||style=\"background:#A0ACB8\"|Closed\n|-\n|[[Siliguri]]||style=\"background:#ffe6b7;\"|[[Bagdogra Airport]]||align=center|VEBD||align=center|IXB ||style=\"background:#9F8170;\"|International{{ref label|h|IXB}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/kolkata/International-status-to-Bagdogra-airport-hailed/articleshow/24001049.cms|title=International status to Bagdogra airport hailed|work=The Times of India|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170105110717/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/kolkata/International-status-to-Bagdogra-airport-hailed/articleshow/24001049.cms|archivedate=5 January 2017}}</ref> || Commercial<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.aai.aero/sites/default/files/national-register/BAGDOGRA%20REPORT.pdf |title=Archived copy |accessdate=11 May 2018 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180511214820/https://www.aai.aero/sites/default/files/national-register/BAGDOGRA%20REPORT.pdf |archivedate=11 May 2018 }}</ref>\n|}\n* {{note label|h|IXB}} The airport has limited international operations.\n\n==See also==\n*[[List of the busiest airports in India]]\n*[[Airports Authority of India]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==Sources==\n* {{cite web | url=http://dgca.nic.in/aerodrome/aero_list.pdf | title=Licensed Aerodromes in India | publisher=[[Directorate General of Civil Aviation (India)|Directorate General of Civil Aviation]] of India | date=10 November 2008 | access-date=3 June 2009 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190926172324/http://dgca.nic.in/aerodrome/aero_list.pdf | archive-date=26 September 2019 | url-status=dead }}\n* {{cite web | url=http://www.aai.aero/allAirports/airports.jsp | title=Airports | publisher=[[Airports Authority of India]] | accessdate=21 February 2016 | url-status=dead | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140618154837/http://www.aai.aero/allAirports/airports.jsp | archivedate=18 June 2014 | df=dmy-all }}\n* {{cite web |url = http://legacy.icao.int/anb/aig/Taxonomy/R4CDLocationIndicatorsbystate.pdf |title = ICAO Location Indicators by State |format = PDF |publisher = [[International Civil Aviation Organization]] |date = 12 January 2006 |url-status = dead |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120905221821/http://legacy.icao.int/anb/aig/Taxonomy/R4CDLocationIndicatorsbystate.pdf |archivedate = 5 September 2012 |df = dmy-all }}\n* {{cite web |url = http://www.unece.org/fileadmin/DAM/cefact/locode/in.htm |title = UN Location Codes: India |work = [[UN/LOCODE]] 2009-1 |publisher = [[United Nations Economic Commission for Europe|UNECE]] |date = 23 September 2009}} - includes IATA codes\n* [http://www.gcmap.com/search?Q=country:IN Great Circle Mapper] - IATA and ICAO codes\n* [http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/india/airbase.htm List of Indian Air Force Stations] at GlobalSecurity.org\n* [http://www.pilotfriend.com/World%20airfield%20database/airfield%20codes/codes9/India2.htm PilotFriend - Indian Airstrips]\n\n== External links ==\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20140618154837/http://www.aai.aero/allAirports/airports.jsp List of airports mentioned by Airport Authority of India]