 Villa|pos=MF|other=at [[Tampico Madero F.C.|Tampico Madero]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=MEX|name=Eleuterio Jim\u00e9nez|pos=FW|other=at [[Tecos F.C.|Tecos]]}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n===Reserve teams===\n{{Main|Club Atlas Reserves and Academy|l1=Atlas Reserves and Academy}}\n\n;Atlas (Liga TDP)\n:Reserve team that plays in the [[Tercera Divisi\u00f3n de M\u00e9xico|Liga TDP]], the fifth level of the Mexican league system.\n\n===Former players===\n\n{{For|further information|Category:Club Atlas footballers}}\n\n==Shirt sponsors and manufacturers==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|-\n!Period\n![[Kit (association football)|Kit]] manufacturer\n!Shirt partner\n|---\n|-\n|1989\u201390\n| Pajarito Sport\n| Bing\n|---\n|1990\u201391\n| Vicmar\n| [[Pe\u00f1afiel (mineral water)|Pe\u00f1afiel]]\n|-\n|1991\u201392\n| Pajarito Sport\n| [[Pe\u00f1afiel (mineral water)|Pe\u00f1afiel]]\n|-\n|1992\u201393\n| Vicmar\n| [[Pe\u00f1afiel (mineral water)|Pe\u00f1afiel]]\n|-\n|1993\u201394\n| [[Umbro]]\n| [[Cuauht\u00e9moc Moctezuma Brewery|Tecate]]\n|-\n|1994\u201395\n| ABA Sport\n| [[Cuauht\u00e9moc Moctezuma Brewery|Tecate]]\n|-\n|1995\u201396\n| ABA Sport\n| No Sponsors\n|-\n|1996\u201399\n| [[Atletica]]\n| [[Corona (beer)|Corona]]/[[Estrella Damm|Estrella]]\n|-\n|1999\u201300\n| [[Atletica]]\n| [[Corona (beer)|Corona]]/[[Coca-Cola]]/[[Estrella Damm|Estrella]]\n|-\n|2000\u201301\n| [[Atletica]]\n| [[Coca-Cola]]/[[Grupo Omnilife|Omnilife]]/[[Corona (beer)|Corona]]\n|-\n|2001\u201302\n| [[Nike, Inc.|Nike]]\n\n| [[Coca-Cola]]/[[Grupo Omnilife|Omnilife]]/[[Corona (beer)|Corona]]\n|-\n|2002\u201303\n| [[Nike, Inc.|Nike]]\n| [[Coca-Cola]]/[[Corona (beer)|Corona]]\n|-\n|2003\u201304\n| [[Nike, Inc.|Nike]]\n| [[Coca-Cola]]/[[Corona (beer)|Corona]]/[[Telcel]]\n|-\n|2004\u201305\n| [[Kappa (company)|Kappa]]\n| [[Coca-Cola]]/Bedoyecta/\n|-\n|2005\u201306\n| [[Kappa (company)|Kappa]]\n| [[Coca-Cola]]/[[BSkyB|Sky]]/[[Corona (beer)|Corona]]\n|-\n|2006\u201307\n| [[Kappa (company)